: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red;\">，配以江南丝竹的渺渺之音，以及升腾缭绕的水雾，让人遁入梦幻的禅境。</span></span></section></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20191206/1575618347699008.jpg\" title=\"1575618347699008.jpg\" alt=\"1575618347699008.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"440\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 440px;\"/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20191206/1575618368111340.jpg\" title=\"1575618368111340.jpg\" alt=\"1575618368111340.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 467px;\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;▲西湾街·静谧夜泊</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(199, 149, 24); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">渔趣后港街、游船南湖街、民宿福洪街</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">等处，帆船造型的灯光勾勒出出船的水乡图景。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(199, 149, 24); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">南湖秋月园</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">栈道芦苇与亭台水榭相映成趣，渲染出夜游江南园林的无穷意韵。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1