</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;\">从城市的喧嚣中抽离，到<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">香村</strong>与朴素的田野为邻，彻底舒展疲惫的身心，享受归园田居的生活。在<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">祁庄</strong>，时代在此定格，不同的院落，定格在不同的年代。</span></section><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20191206/1575619111137934.jpg\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 467px;\" title=\"1575619111137934.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" alt=\"1575619111137934.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20191206/1575619111120781.jpg\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 467px;\" title=\"1575619111120781.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" alt=\"1575619111120781.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">各栋乡宿装饰风格分别对应上世纪</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">60、70、80、90和二十一世纪00年代</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的情怀，家具、摆设舒张有度，特色鲜明，各种装饰细节烙印着年代的印记，却又被现代设计的语言诠释得温暖舒心。更有全新科技智能</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">未来屋</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">智慧民宿，打造黑与白的和谐，光与影的治愈。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20191206/1575619174122059.jpg\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 467px;\" title=\"1575619174122059.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" alt=\"1575619174122059.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20191206/1575619174997777.jpg\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 467px;\" title=\"1575619174997777.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" alt=\"1575619174997777.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; letter-spacing: 1px;\">年代秀&amp;未来屋</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">，每一栋都是一台时光机器，带你体会不同年代的不同风情，重拾那份遗失的美好，品味那股恬淡而温馨的乡愁，释放心底的尘埃。</span></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20191206/1575619221603219.gif\" title=\"1575619221603219.gif\" alt=\"640.gif\"/></p>', '周庄旅游', '1575619226', '1');
